data.description: Northeastern Colorado Springs, Spacious three-bedroom condominium in a gated community. Tiled entry welcomes with natural lighting throughout. Living room with beautiful crown molding, Gas fireplace with wood mantle, Plantation Blinds, ceiling fan, and glass sliding door with mountain views leading to the covered, front, gated patio. Sizable dining area also with glass sliding doors leading to the back patio. Galley kitchen offers tiled flooring and counters, plenty of cabinets and pantry.  Master bedroom with walk-in closet and en-suite with large soaking tub. Conveniently located laundry area, two additional bedrooms and full bath completes the floor plan. Home is located near Powers corridor, Peterson AF Base, shopping, restaurants, schools (district 49), hotels, parks, recreation, public transportation, and emergency response organizations just minutes away.
